<paragraph base="F94966" id="IFRS07_25" principles="no"><paranum>25</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 7"/><data name="paranum" value="25"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS07_P0452">Except as set out in <xref base="F19327963" href="IFRS07_29.dita#IFRS07_29" id="IFRS07_X0416">paragraph 29</xref>, for each class of <xref base="SL37522973" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0115">financial assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0123"/></ph></xref> and <xref base="SL37523036" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0131">financial liabilities<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0127"/></ph></xref> (see <xref base="SL210568" href="IFRS07_6.dita#IFRS07_6" id="IFRS07_X0417">paragraph 6</xref>), an entity shall disclose the <xref base="F16132372" href="../ifrs13/IFRS13_APPA.dita#IFRS13_APPA/IFRS13_P0256">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> of that class of assets and liabilities in a way that permits it to be compared with its carrying amount.</p></body></paragraph>